com.jogamp.common.os

Class MachineDataInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jogamp.common.os.MachineDataInfo

  • public class MachineDataInfo
extends Object
    Machine data description for alignment and size onle, see com.jogamp.gluegen.

    little-endian / big/endian description is left, allowing re-using instances in StaticConfig. Use {@link PlatformPropsImpl#LITTLE_ENDIAN}.

    Further more, the value {@ MachineDataInfo#pageSizeInBytes} shall be ignored in {@link MachineDataInfo.StaticConfig StaticConfig}, see {@link MachineDataInfo#compatible(MachineDataInfo)}.
